Description:
THE GRASS IS ALWAYS GREEN OVER AT HEDGEVALE
"The perfect family home that has a stunning backyard."
The property is located adjacent to Timbertop and within walking distance to St Brigid's Primary School and public transport. Best of all, it's oh so close to Officer's future retail hub that will make Officer such a popular destination.
The near-new double storey property has the ideal floor plan for a first home buyer, young family or even an investor looking to cater for a growing demographic. As a bonus, the synthetic turf makes the property incredibly low-maintenance.
The property features:
- 3 bedrooms, all have walk-in robes;
- The master bedroom has an en-suite plus a parent's retreat;
- Formal living at the front;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Stunning kitchen with a walk-in pantry;
- Study;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage with remote access;
- Massive alfresco overlooking the backyard.
